com.metrics.common.models

Interface IModelCaller

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ModelCallerSearchAdapter

    public interface IModelCaller
    Interface for classes calling scripts. A caller is expected to implement certain methods that support command execution, delivery of parameters, and broadcasting of results.
    Author:
    elangenbach

      • initPagedSearch

        void initPagedSearch(String queryText,
                   String[] fields,
                   Calendar earliestDate,
                   Calendar latestDate)
        A model can ask its caller to perform a paged search on its behalf. Initialize the paged search.
        Parameters:
        queryText - Search text.
        fields - The fields to return. Fields must contain type suffix. See TagUtils.addDataType(). If null, all fields will be returned.
        earliestDate - Earliest allowed date for returned data (inclusive). Can be null indicating no limit.
        latestDate - Latest allowed date for returned data (inclusive). Can be null indicating no limit.
